  "title": "Personal Assistant (Pasir Panjang)",
  "description": "<ul><li><strong>Excellent Welfare and Benefits + Career progression</strong></li><li><strong>Salary: $4000 to $4500 + VB  </strong></li><li><strong>Working location: Pasir Panjang </strong></li><li><strong>Working hours: 9am to 5pm (Monday to Friday)  </strong></li></ul><p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Provide full-spectrum secretarial and administrative support to the Managing Director, including flight bookings, accommodation arrangements, transportation coordination, and schedule management. </strong></li><li>Prepare and compile itineraries, reports, presentations, and business correspondence. </li><li><strong>Organise and coordinate meetings, including preparing agendas, taking minutes, and following up on action items. </strong></li><li>Liaise professionally with internal staff, external suppliers, and clients</li><li><strong>Provide personal assistance to top management when required, such as grocery purchases and coordination of household maintenance. </strong></li><li>Perform any other ad-hoc tasks assigned by the Director. </li></ul><p> <strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Strong verbal and written communication skills, with proficiency in both English and Mandarin as to liaise with relevant counterparts  </li><li><strong>Willing to travel when required </strong></li></ul><p>Candidates are encouraged to apply this position via <strong>Apply Now</strong> button with the following information in the\nresume</p><ul><li>Work experiences and job responsibilities</li><li>Current and Expected salary</li><li>Reason for leaving</li><li>Date of availability</li><li>Education background</li></ul><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p><p>NG DIAUM YEE (R2198031)<br />EA Recruitment Pte Ltd<br />EA License No: 21C0492</p>",
